Possesses the personality and ability to relate to and to establish a mutually respectful relationship with 1) management, 2) peers and 3) the various facility level workers whom are all responsible for ensuring good operations.
The candidate should have a working knowledge of industry and government standards.
Physical Requirements:
Must be able to climb stairs and ladders that ranges from 4 ft. to 200 ft. Must be able to sit at a desk and operate a computer for extended periods of time. Must be able to lift equipment needed to perform work. Must be able to wear safety equipment needed to perform work such as PPE, safety harness, respirator, etc.
